- Or: Same $2.5M AGI from $2.94M revenue vs $3.85M before
- Efficiency dramatically improved

**Better example:**
- Focus on keeping AGI constant or growing
- Current: $2.5M AGI from services at 65% AGI% = $3.85M revenue needed
- Target: $2.5M AGI from services at 85% AGI% = $2.94M revenue needed
- Same AGI with $910K less revenue to manage
- Simpler operations, better margins

