**Client:** "Should we renew?"
**Agency:** "Let's review the year. We increased your MQLs 65%, reduced CPA 30%, and generated $800K in attributed revenue on your $120K investment. That's 6.7:1 ROI. For next year, I see three opportunities to build on this momentum..."
